item.title: Dharan Trip
item.description: It was the time period in life where our friend Bibek Rai came to fall in love with some girl in the college. He was totally in love, thinking only about that girl all day, everytime. We used to wait for the bus in the stand and the girl used wait for the bus with us. He used to catch her glimpse But it was unfortunate that the girl he liked was not so obssesed about him like he was for her.
